title: Happy Hour #4: Cinnamon Roll
itunes:title: Happy Hour #4: Cinnamon Roll
description:
Wind down with us as Anney gushes about sweet cinnamon rolls. No, not the food, the fanfiction tag. Samantha shares her recipe for the cinnamon roll drink and we discuss the cinnamon roll trope, Anney's love for it, and what it has to do with trauma.
